.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, chess, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | chess | fishing | skydiving | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | golf | surfing | tennis |

