.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-7::.
House: cottage, cape-cod, palace, colonial
1. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
2. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
3. the cottage house is between the cape-cod house and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| House   | palace | cape-cod | cottage | colonial |

