.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, scientific, western
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | western | adventure | scientific |

