3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Game   | backgammon | whist | domino | mah-jongg |

