.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, december, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | december | june | august | april |

