2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | june | january | september | february |

