.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-20::.
City: edinburgh, hannover, marseilles, liverpool
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |  2  |     3      |  4   |
| City   | liverpool | edinburgh | hannover | marseilles |

 